Hynden Walch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hynden_Walch 0 Heidi Hynden Walch (born February 1, 1971, in Davenport, Iowa) is an American actress, voice actress, writer, and singer. She is best known for voicing Princess Bubblegum in Adventure Time and Starfire in Teen Titans and Teen Titans Go!
